comments: Irving (BKN) makes contact with Leonard's (LAC) front that affects his SQBR at the start of the drive.
Morris Sr. (LAC) absorbs the contact as he moves parallel alongside Harden (BKN) as Harden begins to drive to the basket.
Beverley (LAC) reaches for the ball and makes contact with Harden's (BKN) arm during his driving shot attempt.
Harden (BKN) momentarily places an arm around Morris Sr.'s (LAC) lower body as they engage during the pick.
Beverley (LAC) commits a take foul on Jordan (BKN).
Brown (BKN) legally contests Williams' (LAC) jump shot attempt.
Morris Sr. (LAC) makes marginal contact with Irving's (BKN) body after the release of his driving shot attempt.
Batum (LAC) places a forearm on Jordan's (LAC) backside as Jordan tips the ball during the rebound and the contact is marginal.
Batum (LAC) legally contests Irving's (BKN) jump shot attempt.
Harris (BKN) makes contact with the ball while he engages with Leonard (LAC) prior to Leonard securing the rebound.
Jordan (BKN) makes contact with Leonard's (LAC) body on the dribble that affects his SQBR.
Mann (LAC) legally contests Irving's (BKN) jump shot attempt.
As Jordan (BKN) and Morris Sr. (LAC) engage during the rebound, marginal contact occurs and they do not restrict each other's ability to rebound.
Morris Sr. (LAC) makes marginal contact with Jordan's (BKN) arm as he taps the ball and completes the shot attempt.
Beverley (LAC) commits a take foul on Harden (BKN).
Leonard (LAC) extends his off-arm into Harden's (BKN) front and dislodges him from his defensive position.
Shamet (BKN) legally contests Mann's (LAC) jump shot attempt.
